******IMPORTANT: READ_ME*******
After EACH press you must wait until the serial monitor reads 
"off" - THEN you must hold down the button just before the cycle restarts. 
If the serial monitor does NOT read "off" after a loop,
you must either WAIT until it does, or restart the upload.

